OL,3,C'Serious failures' by social worker as
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed mother to death
OL,6,FIn a statement, the family of Pamela
OL,7,FNisbet said: "This was an avoidable
OL,8,Ffamily tragedy. We hope that there
OL,9,Fwill be systemic change in the future."
OL,11,FMr Harris said Jersey's mental health
OL,12,Fservices also failed to understand Mr
OL,13,FNisbet's problems and lost
OL,14,Fopportunities to treat him.
OL,16,FHowever, Mr Harris concluded he was
OL,17,F"satisfied that action has been taken
OL,18,Fsince Pam's death to address some of
OL,19,Fthe shortcomings revealed".
