OL,3,C'Serious failures' by social worker as
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed mother to death
OL,6,FChief Officer of Jersey's Health and
OL,7,FCommunity Services, Chris Bown, said:
OL,8,F"The inquest into the death of Pamela
OL,9,FNisbet has found that between January
OL,10,F2018 and August 2019, there were
OL,11,Finadequate steps and failings in the
OL,12,Fassessment and care of Andrew Nisbet
OL,13,Fby mental health services.
OL,15,F"We would like to take this
OL,16,Fopportunity to extend our deepest
OL,17,Fapologies for these failings to Mrs
OL,18,FNisbet's husband and family.
